{"id":530294,"date":[{"year":1973,"month":9,"day":3}],"page":"4","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"风雷激","column":"颂歌声声向党唱","genre":"","count":"177","ytitle":"","mtitle":"水兵的心儿向北京","ftitle":"","authors":["张秉珏"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"东海舰队　张秉珏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"军舰夜泊风浪中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遥望万家灯火红。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欢庆“十大”晚会海上开，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱演个节目《向阳颂》。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海风弹起琴弦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"波涛擂起锣鼓，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"航标灯投来赞许目光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"远处群山翩翩舞。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"政委唱一曲《北京颂歌》，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水兵的心飞向首都；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"舰长唱一首《我爱这蓝色的海洋》，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"表不尽咱自豪和幸福。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浪拍船舷掌声起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"月出云层笑脸露。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要问下一个节目:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看咱驾起战舰去巡逻。"}]}